data.description: Nice split level home featuring 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths and a half bath. The upstairs full bath has recently been remodeled. Beautiful hardwood floors in the living room and hallway. The basement is fully finished with a full bath, could be used as a 4th bedroom or as an in-law-suite or teen suite. Enjoy the covered, screened in back porch overlooking the private, level back yard.
